{
  "texts": [
    "For each Segment, a LLM-based Response Analyzer, described in Section 5.2, is used to classify the Segment into (Dimension, Score).",
    "If CaiTI fails to classify the Segment into the format of 3 and demonstrated in Figure 8.8To ensure the user provides follow-up information in the right direction, an R-V Reasoner and an R-V Guide are deployed.",
    "Based on the user response to the original and follow-up question, CaiTI provides validation, which includes affective reflection and affirmations in MI.",
    "Then, CaiTI assigns the Score to Dimension.",
    "After handling all Segment(s), CaiTI verifies whether the user does respond to the question asked by CaiTI in Dimension_N."
  ]
}